Invocation Name: spencer fortune telling
des:
Ask for a fortune and see what Spencer has to say.

Fortunes are always exciting but shouldn't be taken too seriously.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Spencer Fortune Telling" or "Alexa, open Spencer Fortune Telling" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
